      {
         "id": "SECTION_prerequisites",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><span id=\"htZoomImageMsg\"></span></p><p><span id=\"htAmericaAbyaYalaMsg\"></span> (<htcite0>).</p><p><i>Este texto forma parte de la etapa \"<b>El/los descubridor(es)</b>\" del juego <htcite1> de History Tracers. Recomendamos al lector jugar al menos esta fase para observar la aplicación práctica del método.</i></p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "160fb48c-1711-491e-a1aa-e1257e7889af",
                     "text": "Porto-Gonçalves, Carlos Walter",
                     "page": "pp. 39-43",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "05",
                        "day": "11"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "96f3d3af-15c3-4c37-9d0e-e4b7db0db1db",
                     "text": "Método Científico",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "01",
                        "day": "26"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2011",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
